des:
Go beyond the ordinary and enjoy access to new podcasts and get front row access to the World of Red Bull on your Echo or Alexa enabled device.

Features Include:

Exciting podcasts like:

• How to be Superhuman, examine the super human feats of athletes’ strength and endurance.
• Talking Bull, the official podcast of the Oracle Red Bull Racing Team.
• Beyond the Ordinary, meet the people pushing the boundaries of sport, adventure, gaming, and more.
• Decoding Athletes, find out what it takes to be an elite level athlete.
• And the new podcast, Why I Run, which celebrates the extraordinary and everyday stories of runners as the team for the 2022 Wings for Life World Run is constructed with incredible conversations with athletes.

Inquire about frequently asked questions regarding Red Bull products, the history of the company, and more.

Let Red Bull give you wiiings by purchasing a can from Amazon.com. (This skill uses Alexa Shopping to make purchases on Amazon. Alexa allows purchasing by voice using your default payment and shipping settings. You can set a voice confirmation code, turn off purchasing, and see product and order details in your Alexa app.)

On the go? “Send to phone” will send a link to your Alexa App so you can continue to listen to your favorite content as you walk out the door.

Contact us at https://www.redbull.com/us-en/energydrink/contact-assistant with any feedback.
